F is for "F%#@ this, I'm out" or "F@#$ it, I'm going in" or "Flash" of course.  D is for "Drop 'em"  or death, die, deadly, etc.  The more important thing, however, is that having Ignite before Flash on loading screens and whatnot looks better to me than having Flash before Ignite.  Just look at them.  

{{summoner:14}} {{summoner:4}}  vs {{summoner:4}} {{summoner:14}} 

The first one just looks right and that's clearly what's most important here.  The Flash guy is getting out of that fire like a sensible person instead of jumping into it.
